				<br />
				<br />
				<p>The University of Delhi has released an official notification regarding the examination form-filling process for Regular and NCWEB students of Undergraduate (UG) and Postgraduate (PG) courses for the May/June 2025 session. The notification includes important dates, procedural guidelines, and special notes for students and colleges regarding the registration process.</p>
				<h2>For Semester II (Undergraduate Courses) :</h2>
				<p> Examination Form Opens: January 28, 2025 </p>
<p> Last Date (Without Late Fee): March 15, 2025 (till 11:59 PM) </p>
<p> Last Date (With Late Fee): March 31, 2025 (till 11:59 PM) </p>
<p> Correction Period: April 1, 2025 – April 15, 2025 </p>
<p> Verification by College/Department: January 28, 2025 – May 7, 2025 </p>
<p> Admit Card Generation: From May 26, 2025 </p>
<p> End Term Examinations Begin: June 7, 2025 </p>

<h3> <b>For Semester IV/VI/VIII/X (UG Courses) & Semester II/IV/VI (PG Courses): </b></h3>
<p> Examination Form Opens: January 28, 2025</p>
<p> Last Date (Without Late Fee): March 15, 2025 (till 11:59 PM)</p>
<p> Last Date (With Late Fee): March 31, 2025 (till 11:59 PM)</p>
<p> Correction Period: April 1, 2025 – April 10, 2025</p>
<p> Verification by College/Department: January 28, 2025 – April 15, 2025</p>
<p> Admit Card Generation: From April 30, 2025</p>
<p> End Term Examinations Begin: May 13, 2025</p>
            </article>
